# RF Front-End Transmitter — Project Summary

**Institution:** Government Engineering College, Thrissur  
**Department:** Electronics and Communication Engineering  
**Standard:** Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) | **Band:** 2.4 GHz ISM

---

## What This Project Does

Designs and simulates a complete **Bluetooth Low Energy RF transmitter** that converts a low-frequency digital signal (10 MHz baseband) into a 2.4 GHz radio signal ready for wireless transmission.

Everything was designed and verified using **Cadence Virtuoso** (schematic + layout) and **Calibre** (DRC, LVS, parasitic extraction).

---

