## Complete RF Transmitter Results

After integrating all blocks (Mixer + VCO + Voltage Amp + PA):

| Parameter | Schematic | Post-Layout |
|---|---|---|
| Output Frequency | 2.435 GHz | 2.435 GHz |
| Output Voltage | 334.64 mV | 318.28 mV |
| Output Current | 6.693 mA | 6.366 mA |
| RF Output Power | 2.24 mW | 2.03 mW |
| DC Power Consumed | — | 8.925 mW |
| Transmitter Efficiency | — | **22.7%** |

> Note: Output settled at **2.435 GHz** instead of the designed 2.41 GHz due to inter-block loading effects and parasitics — still within the BLE ISM band (2400–2483.5 MHz).

